---
// Sección: El Precio de Depender del SaaS (Problema vs Solución)
---

<section class="section problem-section" id="problema">
  <div class="container">
    <div class="section-header reveal">
      <span class="section-label">
        <svg width="16" height="16" viewBox="0 0 16 16" fill="none"><path d="M8 1v6M8 11v.01" stroke="currentColor" stroke-width="2" stroke-linecap="round"/><circle cx="8" cy="8" r="7" stroke="currentColor" stroke-width="1.5"/></svg>
        El Problema
      </span>
      <h2 class="section-title">El Precio de Depender<br/><span class="gradient-text">del Software Ajeno</span></h2>
      <p class="section-subtitle">¿Cuánto está perdiendo tu negocio cada año por comisiones, suscripciones y dependencia tecnológica?</p>
    </div>

    <div class="comparison-grid">
      <!-- PROBLEMA -->
      <div class="comparison-card problem-card glass-card reveal reveal-delay-1">
        <div class="card-header problem-header">
          <div class="card-icon problem-icon">
            <svg width="28" height="28" viewBox="0 0 28 28" fill="none"><path d="M14 4l2.5 5 5.5.8-4 3.9.9 5.5L14 16.9l-4.9 2.3.9-5.5-4-3.9 5.5-.8L14 4z" stroke="#ef4444" stroke-width="1.5" fill="none"/><line x1="4" y1="24" x2="24" y2="4" stroke="#ef4444" stroke-width="2" stroke-linecap="round"/></svg>
          </div>
          <h3 class="card-title">El Modelo SaaS Tradicional</h3>
        </div>
        <ul class="problem-list">
          <li>
            <span class="problem-icon-sm">✕</span>
            <div>
              <strong>~$3,600 USD/año</strong> en suscripciones mensuales de software POS ($300/mes promedio)
            </div>
          </li>
          <li>
            <span class="problem-icon-sm">✕</span>
            <div>
              <strong>Hasta 10% de comisión</strong> por cada transacción procesada en plataformas de terceros
            </div>
          </li>
          <li>
            <span class="problem-icon-sm">✕</span>
            <div>
              <strong>Sin acceso al código fuente.</strong> Tu negocio depende de las decisiones de otra empresa
            </div>
          </li>
          <li>
            <span class="problem-icon-sm">✕</span>
            <div>
              <strong>Datos en servidores ajenos.</strong> Tu información de clientes y ventas no te pertenece realmente
            </div>
          </li>
          <li>
            <span class="problem-icon-sm">✕</span>
            <div>
              <strong>Sin personalización real.</strong> Te adaptas al software, no el software a tu negocio
            </div>
          </li>
        </ul>
        <div class="card-bottom-stat problem-stat">
          <span class="stat-number">$18,000+</span>
          <span class="stat-desc">Perdidos en 5 años de suscripción</span>
        </div>
      </div>

      <!-- SOLUCIÓN -->
      <div class="comparison-card solution-card glass-card reveal reveal-delay-2">
        <div class="solution-badge">Nuestra Propuesta</div>
        <div class="card-header solution-header">
          <div class="card-icon solution-icon">
            <svg width="28" height="28" viewBox="0 0 28 28" fill="none"><path d="M7 14l4 4 10-10" stroke="#00e676" stroke-width="2.5" stroke-linecap="round" stroke-linejoin="round"/><circle cx="14" cy="14" r="12" stroke="#00e676" stroke-width="1.5"/></svg>
          </div>
          <h3 class="card-title">Dueño del Código. Dueño del Negocio.</h3>
        </div>
        <ul class="solution-list">
          <li>
            <span class="solution-icon-sm">✓</span>
            <div>
              <strong>Pago único de $2,000 USD.</strong> Licencia perpetua. Sin cuotas mensuales jamás
            </div>
          </li>
          <li>
            <span class="solution-icon-sm">✓</span>
            <div>
              <strong>Código fuente 100% tuyo.</strong> Modifica, escala y adapta sin restricciones
            </div>
          </li>
          <li>
            <span class="solution-icon-sm">✓</span>
            <div>
              <strong>Tu servidor, tus datos.</strong> Desplegado en AWS, DigitalOcean o donde prefieras
            </div>
          </li>
          <li>
            <span class="solution-icon-sm">✓</span>
            <div>
              <strong>Personalización ilimitada.</strong> El software se adapta a tu operación, no al revés
            </div>
          </li>
          <li>
            <span class="solution-icon-sm">✓</span>
            <div>
              <strong>Soberanía tecnológica total.</strong> Cero dependencia de proveedores externos
            </div>
          </li>
        </ul>
        <div class="card-bottom-stat solution-stat">
          <span class="stat-number">$16,000+</span>
          <span class="stat-desc">De ahorro en 5 años vs. SaaS</span>
        </div>
      </div>
    </div>
  </div>
</section>

<style>
  .problem-section {
    position: relative;
  }

  .section-header {
    text-align: center;
    display: flex;
    flex-direction: column;
    align-items: center;
    margin-bottom: 4rem;
  }

  .comparison-grid {
    display: grid;
    grid-template-columns: 1fr 1fr;
    gap: 2rem;
    align-items: stretch;
  }

  .comparison-card {
    padding: 2.5rem;
    position: relative;
    display: flex;
    flex-direction: column;
  }

  .card-header {
    display: flex;
    align-items: center;
    gap: 1rem;
    margin-bottom: 2rem;
  }

  .card-icon {
    width: 52px;
    height: 52px;
    display: flex;
    align-items: center;
    justify-content: center;
    border-radius: 14px;
    flex-shrink: 0;
  }

  .problem-icon {
    background: rgba(239, 68, 68, 0.1);
    border: 1px solid rgba(239, 68, 68, 0.15);
  }

  .solution-icon {
    background: rgba(0, 230, 118, 0.1);
    border: 1px solid rgba(0, 230, 118, 0.15);
  }

  .card-title {
    font-size: 1.2rem;
    font-weight: 700;
    color: var(--text-primary);
  }

  /* Problem Card */
  .problem-card {
    border-color: rgba(239, 68, 68, 0.1);
  }

  .problem-card:hover {
    border-color: rgba(239, 68, 68, 0.2);
  }

  .problem-list, .solution-list {
    display: flex;
    flex-direction: column;
    gap: 1.25rem;
    flex-grow: 1;
  }

  .problem-list li, .solution-list li {
    display: flex;
    align-items: flex-start;
    gap: 0.75rem;
    font-size: 0.95rem;
    color: var(--text-secondary);
    line-height: 1.6;
  }

  .problem-list li strong, .solution-list li strong {
    color: var(--text-primary);
  }

  .problem-icon-sm {
    flex-shrink: 0;
    width: 22px;
    height: 22px;
    display: flex;
    align-items: center;
    justify-content: center;
    background: rgba(239, 68, 68, 0.1);
    color: #ef4444;
    border-radius: 50%;
    font-size: 0.7rem;
    font-weight: 700;
    margin-top: 2px;
  }

  .solution-icon-sm {
    flex-shrink: 0;
    width: 22px;
    height: 22px;
    display: flex;
    align-items: center;
    justify-content: center;
    background: rgba(0, 230, 118, 0.1);
    color: #00e676;
    border-radius: 50%;
    font-size: 0.7rem;
    font-weight: 700;
    margin-top: 2px;
  }

  /* Solution Card */
  .solution-card {
    border-color: rgba(0, 230, 118, 0.15);
    background: rgba(0, 230, 118, 0.02);
  }

  .solution-card:hover {
    border-color: rgba(0, 230, 118, 0.25);
    background: rgba(0, 230, 118, 0.04);
  }

  .solution-badge {
    position: absolute;
    top: -12px;
    left: 2rem;
    padding: 0.35rem 1rem;
    background: var(--accent-green);
    color: #0a0a0f;
    font-size: 0.72rem;
    font-weight: 700;
    text-transform: uppercase;
    letter-spacing: 0.1em;
    border-radius: 100px;
  }

  /* Bottom stat */
  .card-bottom-stat {
    margin-top: 2rem;
    padding-top: 1.5rem;
    border-top: 1px solid rgba(255, 255, 255, 0.06);
    display: flex;
    flex-direction: column;
    gap: 0.25rem;
  }

  .stat-number {
    font-size: 2rem;
    font-weight: 800;
    letter-spacing: -0.02em;
  }

  .problem-stat .stat-number {
    color: #ef4444;
  }

  .solution-stat .stat-number {
    background: linear-gradient(135deg, #00e676, #00d4ff);
    -webkit-background-clip: text;
    -webkit-text-fill-color: transparent;
    background-clip: text;
  }

  .stat-desc {
    font-size: 0.85rem;
    color: var(--text-muted);
  }

  @media (max-width: 768px) {
    .comparison-grid {
      grid-template-columns: 1fr;
    }

    .comparison-card {
      padding: 2rem 1.5rem;
    }
  }
</style>
